// How to bring back minimize and maximize buttons in Gnome 3

// 1.The command line way
// add the values at the left side of : for buttons on the left side "close,minimize,maximize:"

$ gsettings set org.gnome.desktop.wm.preferences button-layout "close,minimize,maximize:"

// add the values at the right side of : for buttons on the right side ":minimize,maximize,close"

$ gsettings set org.gnome.desktop.wm.preferences button-layout ":minimize,maximize,close"


